# After ADR-0001 migration (closes #100, #102):
# - AsurDev is now a subtree (history preserved via git subtree squash-merge).
# - All other submodule entries (home-cluster-iac, roma-execution-bridge,
#   astrofin-sentinel-v5, atom-federation-os, integrations/gitagent) are
#   either ghost (no working-tree presence) or embedded as plain dirs.
#   See docs/ADR-0001-submodule-to-subtree.md.
[submodule "AsurDev"]
	path = AsurDev
	url = git@github.com:mahaasur13-sys/AsurDev.git
	branch = master
